  <section class="styleguide-section">
    <h2 class="styleguide-h2">Display</h2>
    <p>Display utility classes are available for all display values and for all breakpoints.</p>

    <h3 class="styleguide-h3">Notation</h3>
    <p>The classes are named using the format:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><code class="mark">.d-{value}</code>: applies to <span class="mark">xs</span> and up</li>
      <li><code class="mark">.d-{breakpoint}-{value}</code>: for <span class="mark">sm</span>, <span class="mark">md</span>, <span class="mark">lg</span></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Where {value} is one of:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><code class="mark">none</code></li>
      <li><code class="mark">inline</code></li>
      <li><code class="mark">inline-block</code></li>
      <li><code class="mark">block</code></li>
      <li><code class="mark">table</code></li>
      <li><code class="mark">table-cell</code></li>
      <li><code class="mark">table-row</code></li>
      <li><code class="mark">flex</code></li>
      <li><code class="mark">inline-flex</code></li>
      <li><code class="mark">sr-only</code></li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="styleguide-h3">Examples that applies to all breakpoints</h3>
    <div class="styleguide-example">
      <div class="d-inline bg-rc-candy text-white p-2">d-inline</div>
      <div class="d-inline bg-rc-flame text-white p-2">d-inline</div>
    </div>
    <div class="styleguide-code">
      <pre><code>&#x3C;div class=&#x22;d-inline bg-rc-candy text-white p-2&#x22;&#x3E;d-inline&#x3C;/div&#x3E;
&#x3C;div class=&#x22;d-inline bg-rc-flame text-white p-2&#x22;&#x3E;d-inline&#x3C;/div&#x3E;</code></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="styleguide-example">
      <div class="d-block bg-rc-candy text-white p-2">d-block</div>
      <div class="d-block bg-rc-flame text-white p-2">d-block</div>
    </div>
    <div class="styleguide-code">
      <pre><code>&#x3C;div class=&#x22;d-block bg-rc-candy text-white p-2&#x22;&#x3E;d-block&#x3C;/div&#x3E;
&#x3C;div class=&#x22;d-block bg-rc-flame text-white p-2&#x22;&#x3E;d-block&#x3C;/div&#x3E;</code></pre>
    </div>

    <h3 class="styleguide-h3">Breakpoint examples</h3>
    <div class="styleguide-example">
      <div class="d-md-none bg-rc-candy text-white p-2">d-md-none</div>
      <div class="d-lg-none bg-rc-flame text-white p-2">d-lg-none</div>
      <div class="d-none d-md-block bg-rc-spark text-white p-2">d-none d-md-block</div>
    </div>
    <div class="styleguide-code">
      <pre><code>&#x3C;div class=&#x22;d-md-none bg-rc-candy text-white p-2&#x22;&#x3E;d-md-none&#x3C;/div&#x3E;
&#x3C;div class=&#x22;d-lg-none bg-rc-flame text-white p-2&#x22;&#x3E;d-md-none&#x3C;/div&#x3E;
&#x3C;div class=&#x22;d-none d-md-block bg-rc-spark text-white p-2&#x22;&#x3E;d-md-none&#x3C;/div&#x3E;</code></pre>
    </div>
