  <section class="styleguide-section">
    <h2 class="styleguide-h2">Spacing</h2>
    <p>Spacing utility classes are available for <code>margin</code></p>
    <p>Spacing utilities currently apply to all breakpoints there are no responsive spacing utility classes.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><code>mx-a</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>mx-n</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-left: 0 !important; margin-right: 0 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mb-n</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-bottom: 0 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mb-sm</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-bottom: $spacer * 1 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mb-md</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-bottom: $spacer * 2 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mb-lg</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-bottom: $spacer * 3 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mt-n</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-top: 0 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mt-sm</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-top: $spacer * 1 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mt-md</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-top: $spacer * 2 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mt-lg</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-top: $spacer * 3 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.ml-n</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-left: 0 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.ml-sm</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-left: $spacer * 1 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.ml-md</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-left: $spacer * 2 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.ml-lg</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-left: $spacer * 3 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.ml-xl</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-left: $spacer * 4 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mr-n</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-right: 0 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mr-sm</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-right: $spacer * 1 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mr-md</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-right: $spacer * 2 !important;</code></li>
      <li><code>.mr-lg</code> - applies <code class="small">margin-right: $spacer * 3 !important;</code></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="styleguide-section">
    <h2 class="styleguide-h2">Screenreaders</h2>
    <p>Use <code>.sr-only</code> to hide text visually but have it available for screenreaders.</p>
